==English==

===Noun===
'''judge'''  (''plural:'' [[judges]])
# A [[person]] who [[decide]]s the fate of [[someone]] or [[something]] that has been called into question.
# An official of the [[court]] whose duty it is to preside over [[trial]]s and render [[judgment]]s; a [[justice]].

